# Local / personal-private — never include (folder READMEs are tracked; contents are not)
Knowledge/People/*
!Knowledge/People/README.md
Knowledge/Reference/*
!Knowledge/Reference/README.md
Knowledge/Concepts/pm-decisions-log.md
Meetings/
Tasks/follow-ups.md
Agents/_archive/

# Auto-memory (may contain private session facts)
.claude/agent-memory/

# Eval results + primary datasets (private working copies — gitignored by design)
Evals/*/results/
Evals/*/inputs/*.jsonl
# gold.jsonl ships (100-item in-sample set = same content as inputs/snapshots/2026-06-28_gold_pre-split.jsonl)
!Evals/regeval/inputs/gold.jsonl
Evals/memory-consolidation/inputs/*/

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Runtime / local
.DS_Store
*.local
settings.local.json
*.bak

# Private residue term list for scripts/check-repo.sh — never commit
scripts/residue-terms.local
